fr.lirmm.graphik.graal.store.rdbms.rule_applier

Class SQLRuleApplier<T extends RdbmsStore>

  • java.lang.Object
    • fr.lirmm.graphik.graal.store.rdbms.rule_applier.SQLRuleApplier<T>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    RuleApplier<Rule,T>

    public class SQLRuleApplier<T extends RdbmsStore>
extends Object
implements RuleApplier<Rule,T>
    SQLRuleApplier transform rules into INSERT ... SELECT SQL statement when it is possible. If not, it call the apply method of the specified RuleApplier.
    Author:
    Clément Sipieter (INRIA) <clement@6pi.fr>
